The NEWS file for the lwsyslogger package.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
v0.6.3 -- 15 November 2024

Changes:
   Normalized the form for logging IPv4 addresses.

   Fixed a bug that caused traditional BSD-style syslog messages to be
   discarded if they didn't contain a timestamp.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
v0.6.2 -- 14 November 2024

Changes:
   Processor log templates. Added '%r' (relay address) to the set of
   available wildcards. See the lwsyslogger.conf(5) man page for details.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
v0.6.1 -- 14 November 2024

Changes:
   New Processors. Added 'SendMail' and 'UDP'.

   Modular Configuration. Added an 'IncludeConfig=' parameter to the
   '[Global]' section of lwsyslogger.conf(5) to permit modular configuration.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
v0.5.0 -- 1 November 2024

Changes:
   The initial test release.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
